column5: ....for our 3rd son.  He hasn't come yet....and doesn't seem to want to leave, so we're going this morning for induction at 7:30 AM to go get him.  Should be a good day!!  I'll hopefully post a report night!  dk
It will be a great day for ya ... especially when that magical moment arrives.   Hope have have a big enough boat for all those fisherman.   Looking forward to the pics.    All my best !
Good Luck to you Dustin and family!   Whopper
